@page "/"

<div class="Stage">
    <MarketingHero Title="Move anything, "
                   Highlight="anywhere — on demand"
                   Subtitle="Wolfs Trucking Co. is a logistics platform. Tell our agent what you need shipped — a car, a pallet, a container, a single crate — and the agent dynamically composes the legs, drivers, and credentials needed to deliver it. Whoever you are, whatever the cargo, the network adapts."
                   CtaHref="Chat"
                   CtaLabel="Tell the agent what to ship" />

    <div class="HomeWalkthrough">
        <video controls preload="metadata" poster="" playsinline>
            <source src="videos/walkthrough.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <p class="WalkthroughCaption">7-minute walkthrough — voice-narrated tour of the platform.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="Card HomeCtaCard">
        <div class="HomeCtaIcon">📦</div>
        <div class="HomeCtaBody">
            <div class="HomeCtaTitle">Have something to ship?</div>
            <div class="HomeCtaSub">Chat with the agent. The platform composes pickup, legs, customs, and final delivery on the fly.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="Chat" class="Btn">📦 Start a shipment</a>
    </div>

    <div class="Card HomeCtaCard Drive">
        <div class="HomeCtaIcon">🚛</div>
        <div class="HomeCtaBody">
            <div class="HomeCtaTitle">Want to drive for Wolfs?</div>
            <div class="HomeCtaSub">Sign in, then chat with the agent — get matched to the legs that fit your badges.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="Apply" class="Btn">🚛 Sign in to drive</a>
    </div>

    <div class="Card HomeCtaCard Track">
        <div class="HomeCtaIcon">📍</div>
        <div class="HomeCtaBody">
            <div class="HomeCtaTitle">Need to track a shipment?</div>
            <div class="HomeCtaSub">Live GPS, ocean tracking, customs status, and door delivery — all in one feed.</div>
        </div>
        <a href="Track" class="Btn">📍 Track a shipment</a>
    </div>

    <div class="Grid FeatureGrid">
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">🤖</div>
            <h2>🤖 Agent-composed jobs</h2>
            <p>No fixed job templates. Tell the agent what to move; it picks origin, legs, customs, badges, and drivers on the fly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">🧭</div>
            <h2>🧭 Voice navigation</h2>
            <p>Turn-by-turn voice for drivers with live GPS, traffic-aware ETA, and auto-rerouting on congestion.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">📍</div>
            <h2>📍 Real-time tracking</h2>
            <p>Land, ocean, customs, and door — every leg streams live to whoever is watching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">📞</div>
            <h2>📞 Dispatcher you can call</h2>
            <p>Hold the call button and ask anything. Send photos, receipts, or voice — the agent acts on behalf of any driver, customer, or admin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">📎</div>
            <h2>📎 Inline credential intake</h2>
            <p>License, port pass, customs broker letter, team-driver papers — attach as chat bubbles with thumbnails. The agent assigns the right badge to the right leg.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="Card FeatureCard">
            <div class="FeatureIcon">📊</div>
            <h2>📊 Live numbers</h2>
            <p>Revenue, payouts, customs duties, on-time rate, active jobs — all computed from real CRUD events, never seeded.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="Card HomeCenter">
        <h2>🚀 Get started</h2>
        <p>Sign in to start a shipment, drive a leg, or oversee operations.</p>
        <div class="HomeCenterRow">
            <a class="Btn" href="Login">🔓 Sign in</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
